# Gemini CLI Personal Account Configuration
# For API key or OAuth (free tier) usage.

# ─── Option 1: API Key (paid tier) ───────────────────────────────
# GEMINI_API_KEY=ai-your-personal-key-here

# ─── Option 2: OAuth (free tier — no key needed) ─────────────────
# Leave all vars commented to use Google OAuth login

# ─── Model Override (optional) ───────────────────────────────────
GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-pro
